reviewText: Enjoyed watching some of these movies especially when there's nothing on TV, which is when I switch and watch DVDs.. They might not be the highest rated movies, but they were economical to purchase and they were entertaining
Terrible collection.  The movies are not only bad the transfers are bad and the sound quality is horrible.  Avoid at all costs...
Great horror collection.....nice variety in movies.
Good collection of oddities... not the best acting but some decent story lines.
A High School student project poorly done.  So bad I threw it in the  garbage were it should have gone in the first place.
Those movies were pretty bad..so bad, they were funny..however, it arrived on time and in excellent condition..
Some good,some not worth a damn
Some of the movies are very good, some are ok and a couple are bombs, but it is $5!  You can not go wrong on a deal like this.  This collection has some of the better movies in it.
